ygData.messageBody:
Hi everyone,I'm new(You've probably heard this
480 times though)I'm a level 9(extremely close to
10)High Elf,Cleric on Prexus.It feel I've been killing
centurions and slavers for eternity,and I'm level 9!I really
can't imagine how I could get to level 60 without
loosing my mind.Don't think I don't like Everquest though
cause it's the best game I've ever played!Are any of
you on the highest level? I recently took a boat to
the East Commonlands cause orcs weren't giving me
enough exp on level 9. I still don't know my way around
that well but I know to look out for...whatare they
called...oh yeah Griffins.A group I was in got mauled by them
but I casted Divine Aura and ran like the wind! My
bro plays EQ too and he's a Level 27 Troll,Shadow
Knight on Cazic-Thule.Last I saw he's fightin' treants.
Sorry fer speaking so much I'm just pretty bored right
now.See ya!<br><br>Dreevil<br>High Elf<br>Cleric,Level
9<br>Prexus
